  <span class="label">🎨 Image Prompt #1</span>
  <div class="en">An ultra-realistic, cinematic shot of a human brain inside a glass server rack. The brain is glowing with red warning lights and error messages floating around it like 'SYSTEM OVERLOAD'. Stylized tech aesthetic, cyberpunk vibes, 8k resolution.</div>
